title: Camp WeWow Shark Week Day 4
description:
It's Shark Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're playing a round of Two Whats and A Wow!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/game-two-whats-and-a-wow-the-shark-edition for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! Have you overcome a fear?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share how you learned to tackled one of your fears! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!
